ZH: 这家公司去年赢利30%。
EN: This company made a profit of 30% last year.

ZH: 他们希望通过赢利来扩大业务。
EN: They hope to expand their business through profit-making.

ZH: 盈利能力是衡量企业健康与否的重要指标。
EN: Profitability is an important indicator of a company's health.

ZH: 他们赢利源源不断，生意做得很好。
EN: They make profits continuously and their business is doing well.

ZH: 这个行业的竞争非常激烈，要想赢利不容易。
EN: The competition in this industry is fierce, and it is not easy to make a profit.

ZH: 他们的盈利额创下了新纪录。
EN: Their profit figure set a new record.

